article_id:923,category_name:News,title_name:Chapter 11: Android Anguish Added to the Main Campaign![Update],image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a4b869e754ea8b1cb88aa35d1cfe8ed0.png,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577356800"></span>]</strong></span><br>We have confirmed an issue where the game locks up on certain devices when starting the chapter 11 / 6-2 quest &quot;Elimination Protocol&quot; and the chapter 11 EX 1-2 quest &quot;Blocked Path&quot;.<br><br>We plan to fix this issue in a data update on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577772000"></span>. We will update this notification once the fix has been applied.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>Chapter 11: Android Anguish was added to the main campaign at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576476000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a4b869e754ea8b1cb88aa35d1cfe8ed0.png"></div><div>A revived Morsayati has begun conquering the world by slaying any dragons he can locate. Soon, however, he finds himself in possession of ancient combat androids that might be powerful enough to defeat the prince and his friends!</div><div><br></div><div>We hope you&#39;re looking forward seeing what&#39;s in store for the prince and his friends!</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>Chapter 11 of the main campaign, Android Anguish, will unlock if you clear Ch. 10 / 6-3 &quot;A New Vow.&quot;</div><div><br></div><div>Thanks for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1576476000,update_time1577356803